          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="content-guidelines" class="doc-h3">Content Guidelines<span class="h3-badge" style="background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1);color:var(--prism-violet);">Recommended</span></h3>
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
              <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span><ul>
                <li>Close the calendar popover immediately on day click for Single selection.</li>
                <li>Show the Footer Actions for Range selection so the user can confirm or cancel.</li>
                <li>Disable past dates when only future dates are valid (e.g. booking, scheduling).</li>
                <li>Keep the calendar panel above or below the trigger field, with arrow/popover positioning.</li>
                <li>Pre-populate the calendar with the current date or last-used date.</li>
              </ul></div>
              <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span><ul>
                <li>Require a separate "Apply" step for single date selection unless the UI context demands it.</li>
                <li>Auto-close a range picker on end-date click without giving the user a chance to review.</li>
                <li>Show disabled dates without a clear visual or accessible reason.</li>
                <li>Clip the calendar behind other elements or off-screen edges.</li>
                <li>Open the calendar on an arbitrary month with no selection context.</li>
              </ul></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== STYLE ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-style" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <h2 id="style-overview" class="doc-section-title">Style</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens, size specifications, and visual states that define the Calendar's appearance.</p>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="variants" class="doc-section-title">Variants</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">The component set contains 2 variants across one axis.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Axis</th><th>Values</th><th>Count</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><strong>Type</strong></td><td><code>Single</code>, <code>Range</code></td><td>2</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <div style="margin-top:16px;padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.15);border-radius:12px;">
              <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--prism-text);line-height:1.6;margin:0;"><strong>Component property:</strong> <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Show Footer</code> (Boolean, default OFF) &#8212; Toggles the Footer Actions row at the bottom of the panel.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="types" class="doc-section-title">Types</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Single and Range calendar types for different date selection scenarios.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <h4 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:12px;">Single</h4>
                <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:16px;">A single calendar panel for selecting one date. Displays one month at a time. 276px wide &times; 300px tall.</p>
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;">
                  <div class="cal-panel single" style="transform:scale(0.85);transform-origin:top center;">
                    <div class="cal-header">
                      <button class="cal-header-btn"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg></button>
                      <span class="cal-header-title">March 2026</span>
                      <button class="cal-header-btn"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cal-weekdays"><span>Sun</span><span>Mon</span><span>Tue</span><span>Wed</span><span>Thu</span><span>Fri</span><span>Sat</span></div>
                    <div class="cal-grid">
                      <div class="cal-day">1</div><div class="cal-day">2</div><div class="cal-day">3</div><div class="cal-day">4</div><div class="cal-day">5</div><div class="cal-day">6</div><div class="cal-day">7</div>
                      <div class="cal-day">8</div><div class="cal-day">9</div><div class="cal-day">10</div><div class="cal-day">11</div><div class="cal-day">12</div><div class="cal-day">13</div><div class="cal-day">14</div>
                      <div class="cal-day selected">15</div><div class="cal-day">16</div><div class="cal-day">17</div><div class="cal-day">18</div><div class="cal-day">19</div><div class="cal-day">20</div><div class="cal-day">21</div>
                      <div class="cal-day">22</div><div class="cal-day">23</div><div class="cal-day">24</div><div class="cal-day">25</div><div class="cal-day">26</div><div class="cal-day">27</div><div class="cal-day">28</div>
                      <div class="cal-day">29</div><div class="cal-day">30</div><div class="cal-day">31</div><div class="cal-day other-month">1</div><div class="cal-day other-month">2</div><div class="cal-day other-month">3</div><div class="cal-day other-month">4</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <h4 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:12px;">Range</h4>
                <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:16px;">Two calendar panels side by side for selecting start and end dates. 544px wide &times; 300px tall.</p>
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;">
                  <div class="cal-panel range" style="transform:scale(0.52);transform-origin:top center;">
                    <div class="cal-month">
                      <div class="cal-header">
                        <button class="cal-header-btn"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg></button>
                        <span class="cal-header-title">March 2026</span>
                        <span style="width:28px;"></span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="cal-weekdays"><span>Sun</span><span>Mon</span><span>Tue</span><span>Wed</span><span>Thu</span><span>Fri</span><span>Sat</span></div>
                      <div class="cal-grid">
                        <div class="cal-day">1</div><div class="cal-day">2</div><div class="cal-day">3</div><div class="cal-day">4</div><div class="cal-day">5</div><div class="cal-day">6</div><div class="cal-day">7</div>
                        <div class="cal-day">8</div><div class="cal-day range-start">9</div><div class="cal-day in-range">10</div><div class="cal-day in-range">11</div><div class="cal-day range-end">12</div><div class="cal-day">13</div><div class="cal-day">14</div>
                        <div class="cal-day">15</div><div class="cal-day">16</div><div class="cal-day">17</div><div class="cal-day">18</div><div class="cal-day">19</div><div class="cal-day">20</div><div class="cal-day">21</div>
                        <div class="cal-day">22</div><div class="cal-day">23</div><div class="cal-day">24</div><div class="cal-day">25</div><div class="cal-day">26</div><div class="cal-day">27</div><div class="cal-day">28</div>
                        <div class="cal-day">29</div><div class="cal-day">30</div><div class="cal-day">31</div><div class="cal-day other-month">1</div><div class="cal-day other-month">2</div><div class="cal-day other-month">3</div><div class="cal-day other-month">4</div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cal-month">
                      <div class="cal-header">
                        <span style="width:28px;"></span>
                        <span class="cal-header-title">April 2026</span>
                        <button class="cal-header-btn"><svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></button>
                      </div>
                      <div class="cal-weekdays"><span>Sun</span><span>Mon</span><span>Tue</span><span>Wed</span><span>Thu</span><span>Fri</span><span>Sat</span></div>
                      <div class="cal-grid">
                        <div class="cal-day other-month">29</div><div class="cal-day other-month">30</div><div class="cal-day other-month">31</div><div class="cal-day">1</div><div class="cal-day">2</div><div class="cal-day">3</div><div class="cal-day">4</div>
                        <div class="cal-day">5</div><div class="cal-day">6</div><div class="cal-day">7</div><div class="cal-day">8</div><div class="cal-day">9</div><div class="cal-day">10</div><div class="cal-day">11</div>
                        <div class="cal-day">12</div><div class="cal-day">13</div><div class="cal-day">14</div><div class="cal-day">15</div><div class="cal-day">16</div><div class="cal-day">17</div><div class="cal-day">18</div>
                        <div class="cal-day">19</div><div class="cal-day">20</div><div class="cal-day">21</div><div class="cal-day">22</div><div class="cal-day">23</div><div class="cal-day">24</div><div class="cal-day">25</div>
                        <div class="cal-day">26</div><div class="cal-day">27</div><div class="cal-day">28</div><div class="cal-day">29</div><div class="cal-day">30</div><div class="cal-day other-month">1</div><div class="cal-day other-month">2</div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="day-cell-states" class="doc-section-title">Day Cell States</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Each day in the grid is a Day Cell instance with the following visual states.</p>
            <table class="size-table" style="margin-bottom:32px;">
              <thead><tr><th>State</th><th>Visual</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><strong>Default</strong></td><td>Day number in light muted gray (<code>#8893AD</code>), no background</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Hover</strong></td><td>Slightly lighter dark background on the day number (<code>#2A2E3F</code>)</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Today</strong></td><td>Day number with underline indicator to distinguish current date</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Selected</strong></td><td>Filled cyan-blue circle (<code>#38BFFF</code>), white day number</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Range Start</strong></td><td>Filled cyan-blue circle, right half of cell has dark navy band</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>In Range</strong></td><td>Full cell width dark navy band fill (<code>#0F1B30</code>), white text</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Range End</strong></td><td>Filled cyan-blue circle, left half of cell has dark navy band</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Disabled</strong></td><td>Deeply muted text (<code>#4A5368</code>), not interactive</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Other month</strong></td><td>Deeply muted gray, reduced opacity</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <!-- Visual state cards -->
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(140px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="padding:24px 16px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;"><div class="cal-day" style="margin:0 auto;">15</div></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Default</div>
                <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Muted gray text</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px 16px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;"><div class="cal-day" style="margin:0 auto;background:#2A2E3F;">15</div></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Hover</div>
                <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Dark cell background</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px 16px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;"><div class="cal-day today" style="margin:0 auto;">15</div></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Today</div>
                <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Underline indicator</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px 16px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;"><div class="cal-day selected" style="margin:0 auto;">15</div></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Selected</div>
                <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Cyan-blue circle</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px 16px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;"><div class="cal-day range-start" style="margin:0 auto;">9</div></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Range Start</div>
                <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Circle + right band</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px 16px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;"><div class="cal-day in-range" style="margin:0 auto;">10</div></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">In Range</div>
                <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Dark navy band fill</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px 16px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;"><div class="cal-day range-end" style="margin:0 auto;">12</div></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Range End</div>
                <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Circle + left band</div>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px 16px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;"><div class="cal-day disabled" style="margin:0 auto;">15</div></div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">Disabled</div>
                <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">Deeply muted, no click</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="sizes-dimensions" class="doc-section-title">Sizes &amp; Dimensions</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Measurement specifications for Single and Range calendar types.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Measurement</th><th>Single</th><th>Range</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><strong>Overall width</strong></td><td><code>276px</code></td><td><code>544px</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Overall height</strong></td><td><code>300px</code></td><td><code>300px</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Inner grid width</strong></td><td><code>252px</code> (per panel)</td><td><code>252px</code> &times; 2</td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Header height</strong></td><td><code>28px</code></td><td><code>28px</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Weekday row height</strong></td><td><code>36px</code></td><td><code>36px</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Grid height</strong></td><td><code>196px</code></td><td><code>196px</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Footer height (when shown)</strong></td><td><code>52px</code></td><td><code>52px</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Panel padding</strong></td><td><code>12px</code></td><td><code>12px</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td><strong>Day cell approx. size</strong></td><td><code>36px &times; 32px</code></td><td><code>36px &times; 32px</code></td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="design-tokens" class="doc-h3">Design Tokens<span class="h3-badge" style="background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1);color:var(--prism-violet);">Tokens</span></h3>

            <h4 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;">Panel Container</h4>
            <table class="size-table" style="margin-bottom:32px;">
              <thead><tr><th>Element</th><th>Token</th><th>Resolves</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td>Background</td><td><code>Background/BG-Overlay-Dark</code></td><td><code>#1C2133</code> (dark navy)</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Border</td><td><code>Border/Border-Subtle-Dark</code></td><td><code>#2A2E3F</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Border radius</td><td><code>Radius/radius-8</code></td><td><code>8px</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Drop shadow</td><td>&#8212;</td><td><code>0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.32)</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Panel width (Single)</td><td>&#8212;</td><td><code>276px</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Panel width (Range)</td><td>&#8212;</td><td><code>544px</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Panel height</td><td>&#8212;</td><td><code>300px</code></td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <h4 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;">Calendar Header</h4>
            <table class="size-table" style="margin-bottom:32px;">
              <thead><tr><th>Element</th><th>Token</th><th>Resolves</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td>Month/Year text</td><td><code>Text/Text-White</code></td><td><code>#FFFFFF</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Month/Year font weight</td><td>&#8212;</td><td>Bold (700)</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Navigation icon</td><td><code>Border/Icon/Icon-Inverse</code></td><td><code>#FFFFFF</code> (or light gray)</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <h4 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;">Weekday Row</h4>
            <table class="size-table" style="margin-bottom:32px;">
              <thead><tr><th>Element</th><th>Token</th><th>Resolves</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td>Day label text</td><td><code>Text/Text-Placeholder</code></td><td><code>#8893AD</code> (muted on dark BG)</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Font weight</td><td>&#8212;</td><td>Medium (500)</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>

            <h4 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;">Day Cell</h4>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>State</th><th>Element</th><th>Token</th><th>Resolves</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td>Default</td><td>Text</td><td><code>Text/Text-Placeholder</code></td><td><code>#8893AD</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Hover</td><td>Cell background</td><td><code>Background/BG-Secondary-Dark</code></td><td><code>#2A2E3F</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Selected</td><td>Circle fill</td><td><code>Background/BG-Accent-Cyan</code></td><td><code>#38BFFF</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Selected</td><td>Text</td><td><code>Text/Text-White</code></td><td><code>#FFFFFF</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Range Start / End</td><td>Circle fill</td><td><code>Background/BG-Accent-Cyan</code></td><td><code>#38BFFF</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Range Start / End</td><td>Text</td><td><code>Text/Text-White</code></td><td><code>#FFFFFF</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>In Range</td><td>Band fill</td><td><code>Background/BG-Accent-Dark</code></td><td><code>#0F1B30</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>In Range</td><td>Text</td><td><code>Text/Text-White</code></td><td><code>#FFFFFF</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Disabled</td><td>Text</td><td><code>Text/Text-Disabled</code></td><td><code>#4A5368</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Other month</td><td>Text</td><td><code>Text/Text-Placeholder</code></td><td><code>#4A5368</code> (deeply muted)</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== USAGE ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-usage" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="when-to-use" class="doc-section-title">When and Where to Use</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Guidelines for choosing and applying the Calendar component in your interfaces.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>When to use</h3>
                <ul class="doc-list" style="border:none;background:transparent;padding-left:20px;font-size:14.5px;">
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">When the user must select a specific calendar date (e.g. scheduled task, report date, event date).</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">When the user must select a date range (e.g. booking period, filter window) &#8212; use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Type=Range</code>.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">Inside date input fields &#8212; the calendar appears as a popover triggered by clicking or focusing a date input.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;">For reporting filters or query date ranges where two-month visibility helps compare periods.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div style="padding:24px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;">
                <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="#e42527" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>When NOT to use</h3>
                <ul class="doc-list" style="border:none;background:transparent;padding-left:20px;font-size:14.5px;">
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">For selecting a time-of-day &#8212; combine with a Time Picker; do not use the Calendar alone.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">For relative date presets ("Last 7 days", "This month") &#8212; use a dropdown filter instead.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;margin-bottom:8px;">When only a year or month needs to be selected &#8212; use a simpler Month/Year picker.</li>
                  <li style="border:none;background:transparent;">Inline/always-visible calendar for displaying events &#8212; use a full Calendar View component instead.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="single-vs-range" class="doc-section-title">Single vs Range</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Choose the right calendar type based on the selection scenario.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Scenario</th><th>Use</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td>Picking one specific date (e.g. due date, birthdate)</td><td><code>Single</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Picking a start and end boundary (e.g. leave dates, report window)</td><td><code>Range</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>User may clear or leave date unset</td><td><code>Single</code> with an optional clear action in the footer</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Comparing data across a custom time window</td><td><code>Range</code></td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="footer-actions-guidance" class="doc-section-title">Footer Actions Guidance</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">When to enable or disable the footer action row.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Scenario</th><th>Show Footer</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td>Calendar embedded in a form &#8212; the form's own submit button confirms the date</td><td><code>OFF</code> (default)</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Calendar appears as a standalone popover &#8212; user must explicitly confirm before closing</td><td><code>ON</code></td></tr>
                <tr><td>Range picker where tentative selection should be previewed before applying</td><td><code>ON</code></td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="dos-and-donts" class="doc-section-title">Do's and Don'ts</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Guidelines for effective Calendar usage.</p>
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
              <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span><ul>
                <li><strong>Immediate selection:</strong> Close the calendar popover immediately on day click for Single selection.</li>
                <li><strong>Confirm ranges:</strong> Show the Footer Actions for Range selection so the user can confirm or cancel.</li>
                <li><strong>Disable invalid dates:</strong> Disable past dates when only future dates are valid (e.g. booking, scheduling).</li>
                <li><strong>Smart positioning:</strong> Keep the calendar panel above or below the trigger field, with arrow/popover positioning.</li>
                <li><strong>Pre-populate:</strong> Pre-populate the calendar with the current date or last-used date.</li>
              </ul></div>
              <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span><ul>
                <li><strong>Extra confirm step:</strong> Require a separate "Apply" step for single date selection unless the UI context demands it.</li>
                <li><strong>Auto-close range:</strong> Auto-close a range picker on end-date click without giving the user a chance to review.</li>
                <li><strong>Unclear disabled:</strong> Show disabled dates without a clear visual or accessible reason.</li>
                <li><strong>Clipping:</strong> Clip the calendar behind other elements or off-screen edges.</li>
                <li><strong>No context:</strong> Open the calendar on an arbitrary month with no selection context.</li>
              </ul></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="related" class="doc-section-title">Related</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Components that complement or can be used alongside the Calendar.</p>
            <div class="related-grid">
              <a href="Date-picker.html" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg> Date picker</a>
              <a href="Dropdown.html" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg> Dropdown</a>
              <a href="Tooltip.html" class="related-chip"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/></svg> Tooltip</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="references" class="doc-section-title">References</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens and resources for implementing the Calendar component.</p>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li><strong>Figma Node:</strong> <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">17189:1121070</code> &#8212; Component Set: Calendar</li>
              <li><strong>Total Variants:</strong> 2 types (Single, Range) &times; Show Footer toggle = <strong>4 combinations</strong></li>
              <li><strong>Typography:</strong> Zoho Puvi Bold (700) for month/year, Medium (500) for weekday labels, Regular (400) for day numbers</li>
              <li><strong>Sub-components:</strong> Calendar Header (<code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">17189:1120682</code>), Weekday Row (<code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">17189:1120690</code>), Calendar Grid (<code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">17189:1120705</code>), Footer Actions (<code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">17189:1120796</code>)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- ========== CODE ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-code" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <h2 id="live-demo-code" class="doc-section-title">Live demo (Code)</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Configure the Calendar component and view generated HTML.</p>
          <div class="code-playground">
            <div class="cp-toolbar">
              <div class="cp-control-group"><label class="cp-label">Type</label><select class="cp-select" id="pg-type"><option value="single" selected>Single</option><option value="range">Range</option></select></div>
              <div class="cp-control-group"><label class="cp-label">Show Footer</label><select class="cp-select" id="pg-footer"><option value="no" selected>No</option><option value="yes">Yes</option></select></div>
            </div>
            <div class="cp-preview" id="pg-preview-area"></div>
            <div class="cp-code-header">
              <div style="font-size:13.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);">HTML</div>
              <button class="cp-action-btn" id="pg-copy-btn"><svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7v8a2 2 0 002 2h6M8 7V5a2 2 0 012-2h4.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l4.414 4.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V15a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2M8 7H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2v-2"/></svg> Copy code</button>
            </div>
            <div class="cp-code-area" id="pg-code-output"></div>
          </div>
          <script>
          (function(){
            var typeEl = document.getElementById('pg-type');
            var footerEl = document.getElementById('pg-footer');
            var previewArea = document.getElementById('pg-preview-area');
            var codeOut = document.getElementById('pg-code-output');
            var copyBtn = document.getElementById('pg-copy-btn');

            var chevL = '<svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>';
            var chevR = '<svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>';

            function esc(s){ return s.replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;').replace(/"/g,'&quot;'); }

            function buildMonth(month, year, opts){
              opts = opts || {};
              var months = ['January','February','March','April','May','June','July','August','September','October','November','December'];
              var firstDay = new Date(year, month, 1).getDay();
              var daysInMonth = new Date(year, month+1, 0).getDate();
              var prevDays = new Date(year, month, 0).getDate();
              var h = '';
              h += '<div class="cal-month">';
              h += '<div class="cal-header">';
              h += '<button class="cal-header-btn"'+(opts.hideLeft?' style="visibility:hidden;"':'')+'>'+chevL+'</button>';
              h += '<span class="cal-header-title">'+months[month]+' '+year+'</span>';
              h += '<button class="cal-header-btn"'+(opts.hideRight?' style="visibility:hidden;"':'')+'>'+chevR+'</button>';
              h += '</div>';
              h += '<div class="cal-weekdays"><span>Sun</span><span>Mon</span><span>Tue</span><span>Wed</span><span>Thu</span><span>Fri</span><span>Sat</span></div>';
              h += '<div class="cal-grid">';
              for(var i=0;i<firstDay;i++){
                h += '<div class="cal-day other-month">'+(prevDays - firstDay + 1 + i)+'</div>';
              }
              for(var d=1;d<=daysInMonth;d++){
                var cls = 'cal-day';
                if(opts.selected && opts.selected === d) cls += ' selected';
                if(opts.rangeStart && opts.rangeStart === d) cls += ' range-start';
                if(opts.rangeEnd && opts.rangeEnd === d) cls += ' range-end';
                if(opts.inRange && d > opts.inRange[0] && d < opts.inRange[1]) cls += ' in-range';
                h += '<div class="'+cls+'">'+d+'</div>';
              }
              var totalCells = firstDay + daysInMonth;
              var remaining = (7 - (totalCells % 7)) % 7;
              for(var r=1;r<=remaining;r++){
                h += '<div class="cal-day other-month">'+r+'</div>';
              }
              h += '</div></div>';
              return h;
            }

            function update(){
              var type = typeEl.value;
              var showFooter = footerEl.value === 'yes';
              var html = '';
              if(type === 'single'){
                html += '<div class="cal-panel single">';
                html += buildMonth(2, 2026, {selected:15});
                if(showFooter) html += '<div class="cal-footer"><button class="cal-footer-btn secondary">Cancel</button><button class="cal-footer-btn primary">Apply</button></div>';
                html += '</div>';
              } else {
                html += '<div class="cal-panel range">';
                html += buildMonth(2, 2026, {rangeStart:9, inRange:[9,12], hideRight:true});
                html += buildMonth(3, 2026, {rangeEnd:12, hideLeft:true});
                if(showFooter) html += '<div class="cal-footer" style="width:100%;"><button class="cal-footer-btn secondary">Cancel</button><button class="cal-footer-btn primary">Apply</button></div>';
                html += '</div>';
              }
              previewArea.innerHTML = html;

              // Build code output
              var codeStr = '';
              if(type === 'single'){
                codeStr += '<div class="calendar calendar--single" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Date picker">\n';
                codeStr += '  <div class="calendar__header">\n';
                codeStr += '    <button class="calendar__nav" aria-label="Go to previous month">\n      <svg><!-- chevron-left --></svg>\n    </button>\n';
                codeStr += '    <span class="calendar__month-year" aria-live="polite">March 2026</span>\n';
                codeStr += '    <button class="calendar__nav" aria-label="Go to next month">\n      <svg><!-- chevron-right --></svg>\n    </button>\n';
                codeStr += '  </div>\n\n';
                codeStr += '  <div class="calendar__weekdays" role="row">\n';
                codeStr += '    <span role="columnheader" aria-label="Sunday">Sun</span>\n';
                codeStr += '    <span role="columnheader" aria-label="Monday">Mon</span>\n';
                codeStr += '    <span role="columnheader" aria-label="Tuesday">Tue</span>\n';
                codeStr += '    <span role="columnheader" aria-label="Wednesday">Wed</span>\n';
                codeStr += '    <span role="columnheader" aria-label="Thursday">Thu</span>\n';
                codeStr += '    <span role="columnheader" aria-label="Friday">Fri</span>\n';
                codeStr += '    <span role="columnheader" aria-label="Saturday">Sat</span>\n';
                codeStr += '  </div>\n\n';
                codeStr += '  <div class="calendar__grid" role="grid" aria-label="March 2026">\n';
                codeStr += '    <div role="row">\n';
                codeStr += '      <button role="gridcell" class="calendar__day" aria-label="1 March 2026" tabindex="-1">1</button>\n';
                codeStr += '      <!-- ... more days ... -->\n';
                codeStr += '      <button role="gridcell" class="calendar__day calendar__day--selected" aria-label="15 March 2026" aria-selected="true" tabindex="0">15</button>\n';
                codeStr += '    </div>\n';
                codeStr += '  </div>\n';
                if(showFooter){
                  codeStr += '\n  <div class="calendar__footer">\n';
                  codeStr += '    <button class="btn btn--secondary">Cancel</button>\n';
                  codeStr += '    <button class="btn btn--primary">Apply</button>\n';
                  codeStr += '  </div>\n';
                }
                codeStr += '</div>';
              } else {
                codeStr += '<div class="calendar calendar--range" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Date range picker">\n';
                codeStr += '  <!-- Left panel (start month) -->\n';
                codeStr += '  <div class="calendar__panel">\n';
                codeStr += '    <!-- Calendar Header, Weekday Row, Grid for March 2026 -->\n';
                codeStr += '  </div>\n\n';
                codeStr += '  <!-- Right panel (end month) -->\n';
                codeStr += '  <div class="calendar__panel">\n';
                codeStr += '    <!-- Calendar Header, Weekday Row, Grid for April 2026 -->\n';
                codeStr += '  </div>\n';
                if(showFooter){
                  codeStr += '\n  <div class="calendar__footer">\n';
                  codeStr += '    <button class="btn btn--secondary">Cancel</button>\n';
                  codeStr += '    <button class="btn btn--primary">Apply</button>\n';
                  codeStr += '  </div>\n';
                }
                codeStr += '</div>';
              }
              codeOut.innerHTML = esc(codeStr)
                .replace(/class=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">class</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/role=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">role</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/aria-modal=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">aria-modal</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/aria-label=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">aria-label</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/aria-live=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">aria-live</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/aria-selected=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">aria-selected</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/tabindex=&quot;(.*?)&quot;/g,'<span style="color:#38bdf8;">tabindex</span>=<span style="color:#34d399;">"$1"</span>')
                .replace(/&lt;(\/?)(div|button|span|svg|section)(.*?)&gt;/g,'&lt;$1<span style="color:#a78bfa;">$2</span>$3&gt;');
            }
            typeEl.addEventListener('change',update);
            footerEl.addEventListener('change',update);
            copyBtn.addEventListener('click',function(){
              var r=document.createElement('div');r.innerHTML=codeOut.innerHTML;
              navigator.clipboard.writeText(r.innerText).then(function(){
                var o=copyBtn.innerHTML;copyBtn.innerHTML='<svg width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Copied!';setTimeout(function(){copyBtn.innerHTML=o;},2000);
              });
            });
            update();
          })();
          </script>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="component-api" class="doc-h3">Component API &amp; Properties</h3>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>Type</code></td><td>Enum</td><td><code>Single</code></td><td>Calendar type &#8212; <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Single</code> or <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Range</code>.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Show Footer</code></td><td>Boolean</td><td><code>OFF</code></td><td>Toggles the Footer Actions row (Cancel / Apply) at the bottom of the panel.</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="html-structure" class="doc-h3">HTML Structure</h3>

            <h4 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;">Single Calendar</h4>
            <div class="cp-code-area" style="border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:32px;">
              <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar calendar--single"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">role</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"dialog"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-modal</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"true"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-label</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"Date picker"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#94a3b8;">&lt;!-- Calendar Header --&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__header"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__nav"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-label</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"Go to previous month"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span>...<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">span</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__month-year"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-live</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"polite"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><span style="color:#e2e8f0;">March 2026</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">span</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__nav"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-label</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"Go to next month"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span>...<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#94a3b8;">&lt;!-- Weekday Row --&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__weekdays"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">role</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"row"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">span</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">role</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"columnheader"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-label</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"Sunday"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><span style="color:#e2e8f0;">Sun</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">span</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span> ...<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#94a3b8;">&lt;!-- Calendar Grid --&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__grid"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">role</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"grid"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-label</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"March 2026"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">role</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"row"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">role</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"gridcell"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__day"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-label</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"1 March 2026"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><span style="color:#e2e8f0;">1</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#94a3b8;">&lt;!-- ... more days --&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__day calendar__day--selected"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-selected</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"true"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><span style="color:#e2e8f0;">15</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h4 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--prism-text);margin-bottom:16px;">Range Calendar</h4>
            <div class="cp-code-area" style="border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:32px;">
              <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar calendar--range"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">role</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"dialog"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-modal</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"true"</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">aria-label</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"Date range picker"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#94a3b8;">&lt;!-- Left panel (start month) --&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__panel"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#94a3b8;">&lt;!-- Calendar Header, Weekday Row, Grid for March 2026 --&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#94a3b8;">&lt;!-- Right panel (end month) --&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__panel"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#94a3b8;">&lt;!-- Calendar Header, Weekday Row, Grid for April 2026 --&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#94a3b8;">&lt;!-- Footer (optional) --&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"calendar__footer"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"btn btn--secondary"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><span style="color:#e2e8f0;">Cancel</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span> <span style="color:#D19A66;">class</span><span style="color:#56B6C2;">=</span><span style="color:#98C379;">"btn btn--primary"</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><span style="color:#e2e8f0;">Apply</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">button</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span><br>
                <span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&lt;/</span><span style="color:#E06C75;">div</span><span style="color:#ABB2BF;">&gt;</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="css-day-cell-states" class="doc-h3">CSS Day Cell States</h3>
            <div class="cp-code-area" style="border-radius:12px;margin-top:16px;">
              <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">
                <span style="color:#94a3b8;">/* Panel background &#8212; dark theme */</span><br>
                <span style="color:#E06C75;">.calendar</span> {<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">background</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#1C2133</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">border</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">1px solid #2A2E3F</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">border-radius</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">8px</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">box-shadow</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.32)</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">color</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#8893AD</span>;<br>
                }<br><br>
                <span style="color:#94a3b8;">/* Today */</span><br>
                <span style="color:#E06C75;">.calendar__day--today</span> { <span style="color:#D19A66;">text-decoration</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">underline</span>; }<br><br>
                <span style="color:#94a3b8;">/* Selected (Single) &#8212; cyan-blue circle */</span><br>
                <span style="color:#E06C75;">.calendar__day--selected</span> {<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">background</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#38BFFF</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">color</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#ffffff</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">border-radius</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">50%</span>;<br>
                }<br><br>
                <span style="color:#94a3b8;">/* Range start */</span><br>
                <span style="color:#E06C75;">.calendar__day--range-start</span> {<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">background</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#38BFFF</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">color</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#ffffff</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">border-radius</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">50% 0 0 50%</span>;<br>
                }<br><br>
                <span style="color:#94a3b8;">/* In range &#8212; dark navy band */</span><br>
                <span style="color:#E06C75;">.calendar__day--in-range</span> {<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">background</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#0F1B30</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">color</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#ffffff</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">border-radius</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">0</span>;<br>
                }<br><br>
                <span style="color:#94a3b8;">/* Range end */</span><br>
                <span style="color:#E06C75;">.calendar__day--range-end</span> {<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">background</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#38BFFF</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">color</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#ffffff</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">border-radius</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">0 50% 50% 0</span>;<br>
                }<br><br>
                <span style="color:#94a3b8;">/* Disabled */</span><br>
                <span style="color:#E06C75;">.calendar__day--disabled</span> {<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">color</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">#4A5368</span>;<br>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color:#D19A66;">pointer-events</span>: <span style="color:#98C379;">none</span>;<br>
                }
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== ACCESSIBILITY ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-accessibility" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <h2 id="accessibility" class="doc-section-title">Accessibility</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Guidelines for ensuring the Calendar component is accessible across assistive technologies and input methods.</p>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="keyboard-interaction" class="doc-h3">Keyboard Interaction</h3>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Key</th><th>Action</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><code>Tab</code></td><td>Move focus between navigation arrows, day cells, and footer buttons.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>&#8592;</code> / <code>&#8594;</code></td><td>Move focus one day left / right within the grid.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>&#8593;</code> / <code>&#8595;</code></td><td>Move focus one week up / down.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Page Up</code></td><td>Navigate to the previous month.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Page Down</code></td><td>Navigate to the next month.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Home</code></td><td>Move focus to the first day of the current week.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>End</code></td><td>Move focus to the last day of the current week.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Enter</code> / <code>Space</code></td><td>Select the focused date (or set range start/end).</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Escape</code></td><td>Close the calendar popover without committing the selection.</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="aria-attributes" class="doc-h3">ARIA Attributes &amp; Screen Reader Guidance</h3>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li><strong>Role:</strong> Wrap the calendar in <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">role="dialog"</code> with <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-modal="true"</code> and <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-label</code> when it appears as a popover.</li>
              <li><strong>Grid semantics:</strong> Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">role="grid"</code> on the date area, <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">role="row"</code> on each week row, <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">role="gridcell"</code> on each day cell.</li>
              <li><strong>Weekday headers:</strong> Mark with <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">role="columnheader"</code> and full-name <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-label</code> (e.g. <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-label="Sunday"</code>) &#8212; abbreviations alone are ambiguous.</li>
              <li><strong>Selected date:</strong> Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-selected="true"</code> on the active day cell.</li>
              <li><strong>Range selection:</strong> For range start: <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-selected="true"</code> + <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-label="March 9, start of range"</code>. For end: similar. For in-between: <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-label="March 10, in selected range"</code>.</li>
              <li><strong>Navigation:</strong> Month/year display should have <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-live="polite"</code> to announce month changes when arrows are clicked.</li>
              <li><strong>Disabled dates:</strong> Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-disabled="true"</code> and <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">tabindex="-1"</code> &#8212; do not remove from DOM so screen readers can encounter them.</li>
              <li><strong>Escape:</strong> Must close the calendar popover and return focus to the trigger field.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="focus-management" class="doc-h3">Focus Management</h3>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li><strong>On open:</strong> Focus the selected date (or today if no selection). This ensures keyboard users can immediately navigate.</li>
              <li><strong>On close (Escape / Apply):</strong> Return focus to the trigger input field to maintain context.</li>
              <li><strong>Single active cell:</strong> Only one day cell receives <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">tabindex="0"</code>; all other cells use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">tabindex="-1"</code>. Arrow keys move the roving focus.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="color-contrast" class="doc-h3">Color Contrast<span class="h3-badge" style="background:rgba(34,197,94,0.15);color:#16a34a;">WCAG</span></h3>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Contrast verification for the dark calendar panel colors.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:20px;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <div style="background:#38BFFF;padding:28px 24px;text-align:center;color:#fff;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;"><div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;">15</div><div style="font-size:12px;margin-top:4px;">Selected day</div></div>
                <div style="padding:16px 24px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;border-top:1px solid var(--prism-border);"><div><div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);font-weight:600;">WHITE ON CYAN-BLUE</div><div style="font-size:15px;color:var(--prism-text);font-family:monospace;margin-top:4px;">#FFF on #38BFFF</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(234,179,8,0.12);color:#ca8a04;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:100px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 9v4M12 17h.01"/></svg> ~2.8:1</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;font-weight:600;">Shape supplements color</div></div></div>
              </div>
              <div style="background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <div style="background:#0F1B30;padding:28px 24px;text-align:center;color:#fff;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;"><div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;">10 11</div><div style="font-size:12px;margin-top:4px;">In-range days</div></div>
                <div style="padding:16px 24px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;border-top:1px solid var(--prism-border);"><div><div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);font-weight:600;">WHITE ON DARK NAVY</div><div style="font-size:15px;color:var(--prism-text);font-family:monospace;margin-top:4px;">#FFF on #0F1B30</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(34,197,94,0.1);color:#16a34a;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:100px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> 16.5:1</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;font-weight:600;">WCAG AAA Pass</div></div></div>
              </div>
              <div style="background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
                <div style="background:#1C2133;padding:28px 24px;text-align:center;color:#8893AD;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;"><div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;">22 23</div><div style="font-size:12px;margin-top:4px;">Default days</div></div>
                <div style="padding:16px 24px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;border-top:1px solid var(--prism-border);"><div><div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);font-weight:600;">MUTED GRAY ON DARK</div><div style="font-size:15px;color:var(--prism-text);font-family:monospace;margin-top:4px;">#8893AD on #1C2133</div></div><div style="text-align:right;"><div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:rgba(34,197,94,0.1);color:#16a34a;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:100px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg> 5.2:1</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--prism-text-muted);margin-top:4px;font-weight:600;">WCAG AA Pass</div></div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        </div><!-- main-content-inner -->

